node.text:
I got the opportunity to spend a couple of days in the city and deserts of Dubai mainly for photography. I Shot a few videoclips along the trip and honestly i didn't think it would make it into a movie but it eventually did.

Songs used:
Until We Die - WATEVA
Une Simple Histoire - Nils Andreas
@mydubai @visit.dubai #visitdubai

A moon is rising above the midnight sun 🌙 A beautiful moment on the peaks of Swedish Lapland captured on the @sonyxperia 1 III.
.
Crazy what phones these days are capable of. Which one do you enjoy the most 1 or 2 ?

#travelbyxperia @sony.nordic #xperia1III #sweden

node.text:
A morning in the caves of Nynäshamn with the new @sonyxperia 1 III smartphone. A window to the beautiful Knappelskär Archipelago.
.
As a long time Sony photographer I feel at home with the new Xperia as it’s very similar to the cameras I use profesionally. With 16 - 105mm shooting in Raw i can cover all types of photography and I’m very happy to always have it with me in my pocket.

@sony.nordic 
#travelbyxperia #sweden #xperia1iii
